Template-Plugin-Translit-RU version 0.01
========================================

DESCRIPTION

Template Toolkit filter converting cyrillic text into
transliterated one.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Template

IMPORTANT NOTE

This is alpha release of module. Charset tables and other
stuff could be changed in future versions. Method
'detranslit' is not yet implemented. Use this module on your
own risk. All suggestions are welcome.

